unstake.t.sol
├── when the caller is not same as the staker of the sablier NFT
│   └── it should revert
└── when the caller is same as the staker of the sablier NFT
    ├── it should transfer the sablier NFT to the caller
    ├── it should delete streamOwner
    ├── it should update claim amount
    └── it should emit a {Unstaked} event
